!}

= <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> Planned Coup Discovered!
With the presidential elections approaching, Prussian Minister of the Interior Carl Severing has ordered emergency searches of all <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazi</span> and <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> offices throughout Prussia. During the raids, damning evidence was uncovered: the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazi</span> Party headquarters in Munich had ordered <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> units to be placed on high alert for election day. In the event of a Hindenburg victory, these units were prepared to launch a coup d'état, including the planned seizure of military installations and weaponry. The revelation has sent shockwaves through the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span> coalition.
[? if interior_minister == "Wirth": Interior Minister Joseph Wirth of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> is pushing hard for immediate action?]
[? if interior_minister_party != "Wirth": The Interior Minister seems hesitant, worried about Conservative backlash. ?]
- @push_federal_ban: Use our government position to push for a nationwide <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> ban!
- @coalition_consensus: Seek coalition consensus before acting on the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> threat.
- @prussian_only: Limit action to Prussia to avoid splitting the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span>.

@push_federal_ban
    on-arrival: player_choice_sa_ban = "federal"
    go-to: @_resolve_ban_outcome

@coalition_consensus
    on-arrival: player_choice_sa_ban = "consensus"
    go-to: @_resolve_ban_outcome

@prussian_only
    on-arrival: {!
        Q.player_choice_sa_ban = "prussian";
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.85;
        Q.sa_militancy -= 0.05;
        Q.prussian_police_loyalty += 0.05;
        Q.dvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.05;
        Q.dnvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.1;
        Q.left_dissent -= 5;
    !}
    We limit our response to Prussia alone, maintaining the existing <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> ban there while avoiding a direct confrontation within the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span>. This cautious approach preserves coalition unity but allows the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> to continue operating freely in other states. The Conservative partners seem relieved, but the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> and parts of our own membership are frustrated by what they see as insufficient action against the Nazi threat.
    - @end

@_resolve_ban_outcome
    - [? if Q.sa_ban_burgerblock_succeeds == 1 ?] go-to: @outcome_success
    - [? if Q.sa_ban_partial == 1 ?] go-to: @outcome_partial
    - [? if Q.sa_ban_burgerblock_fails == 1 ?] go-to: @outcome_failure

@outcome_success
    on-arrival: {!
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.6;
        Q.sa_militancy -= 0.15;
        Q.nazi_urgency += 10;
        Q.hindenburg_angry_bruning += 30;
    !}
    Success! Despite grumbling from our conservative partners and outright fury from Hindenburg, the federal ban on the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> is pushed through. The paramilitary organization is officially dissolved, its assets seized, and its members forbidden from marching. While this is a major blow to the Nazis, the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> simply goes underground, forming "sports clubs" and "hiking groups" to continue their activities. The political cost is high, but the republic has demonstrated its will to fight.
    - @end

@outcome_partial
    on-arrival: {!
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.75;
        Q.sa_militancy -= 0.10;
        Q.nazi_urgency += 5;
        Q.hindenburg_angry_bruning += 15;
        Q.dvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.1;
        Q.dnvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.15;
    !}
    A partial victory. The ban is enacted, but with significant concessions to the conservatives. The <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> is officially banned, but enforcement is weak and key loopholes are left open, allowing them to continue many of their activities under new guises. The <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span> is strained by the argument, and Hindenburg's trust in our government is further eroded.
    - @end

@outcome_failure
    on-arrival: {!
        Q.nazi_prestige += 10;
        Q.hindenburg_angry_bruning -= 10;
        Q.burgerblock_stability -= 15;
        Q.nazi_urgency += 3;
    !}
    Failure. Under intense pressure from President Hindenburg and the right-wing of the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span>, the proposed ban on the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> collapses. It is a humiliating defeat for the government and a major propaganda victory for the Nazis, who openly mock the state's weakness. Our coalition is deeply fractured by the attempt.
    - @end
